Author: omnomswag
Content: I'm undertaking a humongous feat in modern leftwing criticism of communism. if any of you are familiar w friedrich engels serialized critiques of spd hardliner eugen duhring known as "herr eugen duhrings revolution in science" or simply enough engels pinnacle "anti-duhring" i will make not a vindication on behalf of duhring but a condemnation of both. herr friedrich engels' path towards bourgeois revisionism, in other words an anti-engels. if acquainted w the countless misnomer and falsification uttered by engels in his professional career, contribute to my theses on engels!
